{"tid":2078851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"脫掟磚罪 遭警壓頸男患抑鬱","createTime":"2020-06-25T10:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T12:05:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70378c57b215ee39e923afbe5e854e7badef4970","tid":2078851,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/3NZF633A3XZPNYYYA7DZEBMHOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2F3NZF633A3XZPNYYYA7DZEBMHOI%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=9e2400bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2F3NZF633A3XZPNYYYA7DZEBMHOI%2F&h=f1141808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/3NZF633A3XZPNYYYA7DZEBMHOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n脫掟磚罪 遭警壓頸男患抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-CDSyzZ6Nl8Sc21gWelyywbMN-I=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W5NJ7BMPBHJN3PKVVVOMQEVK2Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-CDSyzZ6Nl8Sc21gWelyywbMN-I%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW5NJ7BMPBHJN3PKVVVOMQEVK2Q.gif&h=c494b218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員謝南偉<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】科大生周梓樂去年11月初在將軍澳墮樓不治，引發市民多區悼念及警民衝突。一名男子被指在銅鑼灣崇光百貨外向警員掟磚，案件昨裁決。裁判官林希維指不信關鍵警員目擊掟磚經過，片段亦證明稱中磚警員沒被物件打中，不接納兩警證供，裁定被告襲警罪脫。被告在庭外透露當日遭警員以膝壓頸兼施放胡椒噴霧制服，因本案及受社會狀況影響而患焦慮症及抑鬱症。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官直指不信兩警證供<br />\n<br />\n被告林耀庭（35歲）散庭後和親友相擁時雙眼通紅，一度哽咽說「對唔住」。他在庭外謂，獲悉脫罪後鬆一口氣，「情緒一下子湧上嚟」，亦對家人擔心他感過意不去。他表示不評論裁判官質疑警員作供不可信，只謂：「佢哋知道自己講乜。」<br />\n<br />\n被告指當日遭警員以膝壓頸兼施放胡椒噴霧制服，事後見警員巡邏會<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\nwater」。他亦對纏訟的手足打氣：「加油，無論決定係點，我都會支持。」<br />\n<br />\n林官裁決指，從去年11月8日案發晚的傳媒片段可見，涉案警署警長魯君樑及警員謝南偉案發時均向右望，掟磚者卻在二<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n，但片段看不到有市民在魯身邊，市民亦在他開始追趕後散開，與魯聲稱版本相反。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2509/19"},{"pid":"947f676af198a8c0cef23a216134666f23bcbccc","tid":2078851,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"借個位 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立會事實處 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072298</a><br />\n眾志 蘋果 DW德國之聲訪問手足 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2063033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2063033</a><br />\n抗爭文獻館 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2071555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2071555</a><br />\n暴政粵譯 第六課 小心那些準軍事組織 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058004</a>"},{"pid":"c7f6604dc2d75f0ec505c33c2e545d8a915e2a16","tid":2078851,"uid":240004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"快D走出陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1856f9b4dfd2bc65613a3ce3410c8a44bc5b03a1","tid":2078851,"uid":189523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好休息下 放鬆心情先"},{"pid":"42fd27389d78050c0f183f1e95a5850b99d1eb3f","tid":2078851,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"手足加油"},{"pid":"5c059b8238657bb60ecbe34ab8874f11ea4bc085","tid":2078851,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:05:08.000Z","msg":"香港人支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}